refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;




   callback



     The autoload function being unregistered.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.5.0

     Passing the spl_autoload_call function as
     a callback argument to unregister all autoloaders has been
     deprecated. Instead iterate over the return value of
     spl_autoload_functions and call
     spl_autoload_unregister on each value.
